0.91-1 unstable (21/03/2004)
----------------------------
New Features
    * Safe Mode support during install (Patched by DSword - Miikka Koskinen)
    * New YaPiG's documentation look. 
Fixed Bugs
    * Up and Next Page bugs (#915541) 
    * deleted pepeeee debug line on JS of template file zoom_bar.php (#906664)
    * Now GD 1.6 tested and really supported (didn't work on previous versions)
    * messages.log now is on SECURE_DIR (#862986)
    * Install bugfixes
    * Little bug on upload.php

0.91 unstable (28/02/2004)
--------------------------
New Features
    * Updated Spanish Translation.
    * Image Captions/Description. Now you can add a little description of the 
      image contents. (Feature Request)
    * Admin can delete user comments (Feature Request)
    * Admin can modify user comments (Feature Request)

Fixed Bugs
    * Security on comments log (Bug #862986)
    * Warn about possible problem of memory lack (Bug #904278)
    * Delete phid comments: Gallery Comments Counter updated (Bug #888124)
    * Minor bugfixes
    
0.90-1 unstable (20/02/2004)
----------------------------
Fixed Bugs
    * Thomas Orieux JavaScript patch. Now, Resizing works on some browsers.

0.90 unstable (14/02/2004)
--------------------------
New Features
    * Autoresize big images using a JavaScript. Zoom in and out.
    * Admin can show/hide comments and comments form in each gallery.
    * Admin user can upload files using the web admin tool.
      (Based on Matt Thompsom patch against 0.83beta)
    * Admin user can create directories for galleries using the web admin tool.
    * Added Swedish translation. Thanks to Daniel Ek
    * Added Italian translation. Thanks to Andrea Baldon.
    * Added Russian translation. Thanks to Arseny Vesnin.
Fixed Bugs
    * Count hits using gallery navigation bar.
    * Repaired select thumbnail.
    * Repaired view info link in modify image list
    * Removed line with '=>' in counter files
    
0.83beta (30/01/2003)
---------------------
New Features
   * No new features.
Fixed Bugs
   * Counters didn't work properly.
   * Repaired CSS class in view image.


0.82beta (24/01/2004)
---------------------
New Features
    * Added French translation. Thanks to Thomas Oirieux 
      (ttp://flying.disc.chez.tiscali.fr/index.php) and David Foucher both of
      them sent me a french translation.
    * Added German translation. Thanks to docviper (www.docviper.net/photo)
    * Added checking correct GD library is available during installation.
    * Try to load GD library if not already loaded. 
    * Improved install documentation.
    
Fixed bugs
    * Register globals problems when set off (default in new PHP versions).
    * Corrected links in Modify Gallery.
    * Problems using cookies and logout links.
    * Removed annoying \' on comments. Now appears only ' character.
    * Problems with imagenames that have some 'rare' characters as ?,!...
    * Correct link in delete_gallery.php for Delete more galleries.
    * Minor bugfixes.
    
0.81beta (7/1/2004)
-------------------
New Features
    * None. In this version only bug fixing changes.
    
Fixed bugs
    * delete_gallery_form.php, PHP extension missing.
    * Problem setting enviroment variable LANG in some safe mode configs.
    * Multiple-page galleries TERRIBLE BUG! :$

0.80beta (19/12/2003)
---------------------
New Features
    * New template look.
    * Changed from alfa to beta status.
    * Added posibility to gallery logout. 
    * Deleted gallery in admin improved. Now admin can choose what data 
      want to delete (all gallery comments,visits...)
    * Admin can choose gallery thumbnail
    * Admin can add and delete individual images from gallery.
    * Allow multiples pages per gallery. Nice for big galleries.
    
Fixed Bugs
    * modify_gallery.php error
    * Spanish translation problems
    * Some other minor bugs
    
0.72a (5/december/2003)
-----------------------
 New Features
   * Added gallery navigation bar, (that is previous and next gallery links) 
   * Added comments as documentation to template files.
   * Source Code prepared to have phpDocumentor documentation 
     (http://phpdocu.sf.net)
   * Real thumbnail of a password protected gallery shown when user already
     logged in.
   * Updated user documentation (+ Added INSTALL and CHANGELOG files)
   
 Fixed Bugs
   * Problem with access to password protected galleries in some servers
   * Author on comments not shown.
   * Some other minor Bugfixes.

